Package com.gamelanlabs.chimplecrowd.solvers

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FastMHSolver
    Very fast (and just as correct) Metropolis-Hastings solver that uses some speedups.
    MatlabMetropolisHastingsSolver
    MATLAB interface to the solver.
    MetropolisHastingsSolver
    (Correct) traceMH solver.
    PriorSolver
    Runs the generative model "forward" to obtain the prior distribution.
    SamsaraSolver
    Hybridized traceMH + proportional death/particle filter population solver.
    Solver
    All solvers should extend this base class.
